\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces Experimental pipeline for MLLM-assisted classroom behavior annotation. Bounding-box crops are annotated by two 7B-scale MLLMs, converted into pseudo-label sets through filtering strategies, and used to fine-tune CLIP with linear probing or LoRA. The same pipeline also yields annotation-quality and retention diagnostics.\relax }}{7}{figure.caption.18}\protected@file@percent }
